creator: Toni Kroos Academy
descriptionHtml:
I will make you a better football player! Practice videos, insights, coaching feedback, football camps and much more.

Here you can find out everything about my game and my experiences. From the beginnings at youth level to winning the Champions League and World Championship. In high-quality videos I show you the techniques and exercises that have really brought me further.
The training app that really makes you better

• The first football app with personalized feedback - from academy coaches worldwide.
• Train together with me, your friends and the entire world.
• Send me your questions and have a chance to receive my feedback on your game.

360° Toni Kroos - Insights into every part of his career
• All drills are selected myself and are shown and explained through videos.
• Understand my perspective on football through tactical analysis and become a strategist on the pitch.
• Exclusive interviews on all areas of my career - authentic and up close.
• Private stories from the locker room and private situations.
descriptionShort: Make me your coach! Learn what matters in football - on and off the court.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Welcome to the first version of the Toni Kroos Academy App. Before getting started I want to show you the purpose and features of my application and the academy in general.
I will show you a different element every day and give you the opportunity to get insights into my life and learn from my knowledge and experiences in football.
Have fun and see you there!
Toni
